    <ingredient>500gms pasta cooked per directions</ingredient>
    <ingredient>200gms kalamata olives</ingredient>
    <ingredient>300-400 gms chopped salami </ingredient>
    <ingredient>2 cans chopped tomatoes </ingredient>
    <ingredient>2 TBsp oregano </ingredient>
    <ingredient>salt and pepper to paste</ingredient>
    <ingredient>2-3 cups grated cheese </ingredient>

    <step>
Place cooked pasta and all other ingredients, except cheese in heat proof bowl and mix well. Sprinkle cheese on top and place in preheated oven for 1/2 hour.
    </step>
